 scrum master certification can do for you - The term servant leader is the one most commonly associated with the role of the scrum master. </p> <p>Below is an excerpt where he explains the concept: The servant-leader is servant first…It begins with the natural feeling that one wants to serve, to serve first. This term was first described by Robert K. Greenleaf in an essay entitled The Servant as Leader. </p> <p></p>";s:7:"keyword";s:40:"dream theater   metropolis part 1 lyrics";s:5:"links";s:2278:"<a href='https://www.pathshala.co/forum/page.php?id=d7382a-'></a>,
